  "texts": [
    "By referring to the occurrence table of NB algorithm, it can be found that the recommendation rate of NB algorithm on datasets in the medical and biological fields is relatively high, which is 60.0 and 50.0% respectively, while the recommendation rate on datasets in the general field is only 4.8%.",
    "Through the above exploratory analysis, we have a preliminary understanding of the algorithm applicability.",
    "In order to further discover the hidden feature knowledge in the algorithm applicability, this paper uses stepwise regression and decision tree C4.5 algorithm to build a model, so as to find the features and rules that need to be further analyzed and discussed in the previous exploratory statistical analysis.",
    "Modeling memory usage of 8 algorithms on different datasets.",
    "Zhang et al. 10.3389/fncom.2024.1345575 Frontiers in Computational Neuroscience 08 frontiersin.org"
  ]
}